"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In 1965 Argentine artists Marta Minujín and Rubén Santantonín created “La Menesunda” recognized as being the first instalation art.\\n\\n“La Menesunda” revolutionized Buenos Aires, attracting a large number of visitors and several news reports, and is now considered one of the greatest milestones in the history of Argentine art.\\n\\n![La Menesunda (1965), One of the rooms in the installation included a young couple lying in bed.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wZqp7rpZrq12zbfVF9tIb.png?height=408&width=640)\\n\\nThe role of instalation art is to change the perception of a space. This definition resonated with me — a lot. I’ve always had trouble understanding what is it about concept art that drawns me to it.\\n\\nEver since I’ve read Vitalik Butherin’s [Crypto Cities](https://vitalik.ca/general/2021/10/31/cities.html) essay I had [CityDAO](https://citizen.citydao.io/) on my mind. I knew I wanted to participate, but I just couldn’t articulate the reasoning. I now know why. It isn’t an investment at all! It’s the first time we are going to think about a piece of land completely differently. A collection of dust, rocks, and water directly be mapped to a virtual representation. It reminds me of the Japanese crypto punk bazaars where someone created 3D scans of different pieces of rocks from Tokyo and sold them on CDs. \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/MTySPvjlSW_0uOXj7su2F.png?height=350&width=700)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1636437872,\"title\":\"Why my stake in CityDAO is about participating in an experimental new art form \"},\"digest\":\"h4zt8zGm-Ew8QHI2Pzeq3pWcxNuDZYnXs4-EL4kUOkQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5Cee05c642aC2Eb4fb2bDaeCCb55E6dd3A01726d\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3oQSfuCgFSAhYwE_Mt1V9gNbTgl1CW5jodOKivNpPE4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"QFTNiF-BWpJ6WFW-B1I50LAp8-Oee-r0dw3RDF8s5b8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Kz7_l517kQn__qTExDQ8jD5hXlN4L47Ld3ga7pqr5zIGxEdvzmxeKU_Xm4osPG6XeKxRBtwi2lGDh8lOi5aKFQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x51a1da7d16e439e7467f0f7bb5a4096d5e4d2b6c486ec119371d7c5cb6cb2a7c242493397f75df8ac33bf7e9ba48190ecbcac78633f8d856292576a532275e8d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3oQSfuCgFSAhYwE_Mt1V9gNbTgl1CW5jodOKivNpPE4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"QFTNiF-BWpJ6WFW-B1I50LAp8-Oee-r0dw3RDF8s5b8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"a-xvKEZuLcxe6JDTn_zIhl_aLx-ahHuDsA5cZjEJGKY\"}"